description: This Tutorial contains learning main 5 Axis CNC operations. The user will be able to create main 5 Axis CAM operations for CNC 5x Machine Tools with TopSolid7 CAM 5 Axis. This Course is usefull for user who knows how to use TopSolid7 CAM 2-3 axis. Students are able to download TopSolid (*.TopPkg) files and *.x_t format (parasolid) CAD files which used in tutorials. Videos are about 80 minutes with main options and depand explenations. The course include main kind of 5x CNC operations, that's why it will be usefull for TopSolid7.9'CAM users in Industry.
title: Easy Learn CNC 5axis CAM applications for TopSolid 7.9 users
